				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>	

	<div id="dollar">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1">					
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
					<p class="dollarTitle">Give every dollar a purpose</p>
					<p class="dollarText">By assigning purpose to your monry, you'll not only find yourself saving for anticipated expenses, but you'll also find extra money for fun.</p>
					
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1">					
				</div>
				
				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3">
