				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
					<p class="lockTitle">Securely connect to your bank</p>
					<p class="lockText">Foresight Budgets uses a safe, secure bank account connection tool called Plaid to import your transaction history.</p>
					
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>	

