				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
					<p class="alertsTitle">Stay on track with proactive alerts</p>
					<p class="alertsText">Never lose control of your budget again. With proactive alerts, you'll be notified when transactions need to be categorized.</p>
					
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div id="future-months">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1">					
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
					<p class="monthsTitle">See helpful, accurate graphs</p>
					<p class="monthsText">Foresight Budgets will never show you inaccurate or misleading information. Helpful graphs will be available on there is enough data for them to be accurate.</p>
					
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-1 col-sm-1">					
				</div>
				
				<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-3">
