					<img class="lock-img" src="images/icon-text-categorization.png">
						
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6">
					<p class="alertsTitle">Categorize purchases by texting</p>
					<p class="alertsText">Customizable text alerts will help you categorize transactions quickly and accurately before you forget what a purchase was for.</p>
					
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
